This paper deals with the automatic detection of defects in images of photovoltaic cells using machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of Support Vector Machines (SVM) and Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN), which are common machine learning algorithms used in image classification tasks. This suggests that the paper could also fit into categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which could place it in the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) category.
